sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server

    Note over Client: State: Closed
    Note over Server: State: Closed

    Server->>Server: listen()
    Note over Server: State: Listen

    Client->>Server: SYN (connect())
    Note over Client: State: SynSent

    Server->>Client: SYN-ACK
    Note over Server: State: SynReceived

    Client->>Server: ACK
    Note over Client: State: Established

    Server->>Server: receive(ACK)
    Note over Server: State: Established
